Package: clawboot
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Imran Duratbegovic <imranduratbegovicc@gmail.com>
Depends: ca-certificates, curl, git, sudo, tar, zstd, python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-webkit2-4.1, desktop-file-utils, hicolor-icon-theme, systemd
Description: Graphical OpenClaw setup for Raspberry Pi 5
 ClawBoot installs OpenClaw, a local Gemma 4 E2B model, and optional
 Telegram or WhatsApp messaging through a simple desktop wizard.
 No terminal interaction is required.
